    "long_instructions": "## AI as a Technical Expert\r\n\r\nUse AI Chat to fact check a historical event, recite a quote, or verify a scientific concept.\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n1. Find the section in your **Unit Guide** labeled \"Providing historical or technical information\". \r\n2. Choose one of the questions below and rank how well you think a human would do.\r\n3. **Copy and paste** the prompt into AI Chat.\r\n4. Press **Send**.\r\n5. Then read **AI Chat's response**.\r\n\r\n**Try it out!**\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\nChoose one of the questions below. Click to expand:\r\n\r\n::: details [**Fact Check a Historical Event**] \r\n>Who was the first woman to fly solo across the Atlantic Ocean?\r\n\r\nOR\r\n\r\n>When was the lightbulb invented, and by whom?\r\n:::\r\n\r\n::: details [**Look Up a Famous Quote**]\r\n>Give me a motivational quote by Maya Angelou.\r\n\r\nOR\r\n\r\n>What is a famous quote from Albert Einstein?\r\n:::\r\n\r\n::: details [**Verify a Scientific Concept**]\r\n>Explain how photosynthesis works in one paragraph.\r\n\r\nOR\r\n>What is the freezing point of mercury?\r\n:::\r\n",
